633
01:46:06,016 --> 01:46:10,037
I will say, I am incredibly grateful to our counseling team.

634
01:46:10,237 --> 01:46:13,518
They are working constantly throughout the day.

635
01:46:14,019 --> 01:46:15,299
I have never seen them work harder.

636
01:46:15,799 --> 01:46:19,761
They are one of the smartest counseling teams that I've seen and worked with.

637
01:46:22,342 --> 01:46:25,023
I don't think the answer is always to add more counselors.

638
01:46:26,155 --> 01:46:36,406
I think that we all need to work together, but right now comparing us to other schools, every school would say they always want more counselors.

639
01:46:37,868 --> 01:46:47,618
So I think the other question I have is, is it clear to students and families how to engage with these supports at school?

640
01:46:48,516 --> 01:46:51,357
So we've heard from students this week that they don't know.

641
01:46:51,838 --> 01:46:54,019
