642
01:46:54,059 --> 01:46:56,240
We have an advisory coming up this Thursday.

643
01:46:56,260 --> 01:46:58,841
A lot of it will be, who are the counselors in the building?

644
01:46:58,901 --> 01:46:59,641
How do you get to them?

